00:00:05.879 --> 00:00:07.500
and inside that development environment,

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.185
we install Python and got our packages running.

00:00:10.185 --> 00:00:13.169
Next, we went through and we learned about makefiles and

00:00:13.169 --> 00:00:16.259
how makefiles are very powerful but old

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:18.675
technology that allows us to put

00:00:18.675 --> 00:00:23.205
multiple commands together and package them into a logical runner.

00:00:23.204 --> 00:00:25.469
Next, we went to installing Docker.

00:00:25.469 --> 00:00:27.209
So inside of Docker,

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:32.204
